snippet.title: Teeter (Official Game Trailer)
snippet.description:
A ball, a bar, a peg, and a hole. Mundane as individual forms, yet in concert together: magical. Devoid of ads and in-app purchases, Teeter is a beautiful combination of impeccable design and innovative game mechanics that provide players with a singular experience that can only be found on the App Store.

Enhanced controls for 3D Touch supported devices, this game is a whimsical delight.

Guiding a ball into a hole has never been more innovative, challenging, or super fun. 

Oxford comma for the win!
